STATE
v.
Oakland McCULLOCH. No. 24P16-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Bruce T. Cunningham, Jr., Southern Pines, for McCulloch, Oakland. Ryan Christopher Zellar, for State of North Carolina. Kathleen N. Bolton, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Amanda S. Zimmer, Southern Pines, for McCulloch, Oakland. William R. West, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

*901The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of January 2016 by State of NC for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Dissolved by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
